{ Once again, jumping in with the knight is the correct approach. The threat of ...Ne3+ forces White to spend some time preventing it. }
19. Nd5 Be6
{ Yet again, keeping White busy as the threat of ...Bxd5 followed by ...Ne3+ is restored. }
20. Kf2 Rae8
