14. Nxc6 { The sensible continuation of the previous moves. } 14... bxc6 15.
Qxc6 Bxe2 16. Re1 Bc4
{ The bishop returns just in time, guarding itself and the pawn on d5. With ...Rc8 coming next, our position is completely fine. }
