14. Nd2
{ As we have played ...d4, the knight returns to d2 in order to finally trade our menacing knight. }
14... Nxd2
{ White can capture in a variety of ways, by either bishop or queen, or even interpose Nxb6 first. Still, the play is remarkably similar in all variations as we aim to exchange light-squared bishops by ...Bd5 and castle our king. }
