14... Ng4+
{ As it turns out, there is no winning discovery so we should pay some attention and save our pieces instead. }
15. Kh1 Qc5
{ Everything is well protected, and we shouldn't forget we are one pawn up. }
16. Rad1 Be6
{ We are almost fully mobilized, and it is up to White to find compensation in the mayhem. }
