{ A crafty move, asking where the bishop would like to go. Depending on our next move, White will make up their mind about where to develop the pieces. On the flip side, the queen on c2 can be awkwardly placed, as it might come under attack by one of our minor pieces early on.   9.Nc3  is a direct transposition to the chapter Fianchetto with Nc3 – 9.dxc5 Bxc5. }
